title: Mirrors.Edge.Catalyst.with.Update.2.Eng.Repack
description:
==========
Mirror's Edge Catalyst
==========
Genre: Third-Person Action
Developer: DICE (Digital Illusions CE) 
Publisher: Electronic Arts 
Release Date: June 7, 2016
================
About This Game
================
Mirror's Edge Catalyst is the highly-anticipated follow-up to 2008's breakthrough action game, rebooting the franchise for the next generation with advanced visuals and an all-new origin story for Faith.
===============
How to install:
===============
After download is done:
- open Mirrors.Edge.Catalyst.with.Update.2.Eng.Repack,(executable file)
- choose location ,
- click install ,
- wait until is done ,
- play game from desktop shortcut
